WEBVTT

1
00:00:29.038 --> 00:00:30.108
Come on.

2
00:00:33.248 --> 00:00:36.318
Let's go to our home.

3
00:01:46.188 --> 00:01:48.188
You dropped it at the bus station.

4
00:01:51.688 --> 00:01:54.288
(Six missed calls from Landlord)

5
00:01:55.458 --> 00:01:58.628
You called me so many times.

6
00:01:59.727 --> 00:02:00.768
Yes.

7
00:02:02.238 --> 00:02:03.667
I called you a lot.

8
00:02:43.308 --> 00:02:45.547
Would it be all right if I shower first?

9
00:02:46.047 --> 00:02:47.308
I sweated too much.

10
00:02:47.808 --> 00:02:49.577
Yes. Go ahead.

11
00:02:50.118 --> 00:02:51.118
Okay.

12
00:02:57.357 --> 00:02:58.528
Why...

13
00:02:59.387 --> 00:03:00.487
Yes?

14
00:03:00.727 --> 00:03:02.658
Why are you following me in?

15
00:03:04.658 --> 00:03:06.727
I didn't follow you.

16
00:03:14.737 --> 00:03:16.707
I didn't realize.

17
00:03:17.838 --> 00:03:20.077
Yes, I figured as much.

18
00:03:21.818 --> 00:03:24.218
You should go wash up.

19
00:03:38.197 --> 00:03:40.098
(Come to YOLO Cafe, 24. Complaint: Stalking)

20
00:03:42.898 --> 00:03:46.267
He's the suspect of Namgang Station Kidnap case.

21
00:03:47.308 --> 00:03:49.977
The one that stalked a university student?

22
00:03:50.077 --> 00:03:53.248
The details match, including the wrench.

23
00:03:54.848 --> 00:03:58.148
Then why didn't you tell me?

24
00:03:58.618 --> 00:03:59.987
Didn't you know earlier?

25
00:04:00.248 --> 00:04:02.688
You said it was hard for you to find that job.

26
00:04:03.387 --> 00:04:05.357
I couldn't be too hasty at informing you.

27
00:04:06.227 --> 00:04:09.227
It would have been better if you tipped me off.

28
00:04:09.827 --> 00:04:13.197
I could have acted oblivious while watching over him.

29
00:04:13.197 --> 00:04:17.468
You? Act oblivious?

30
00:04:17.937 --> 00:04:19.067
What is it?

31
00:04:19.408 --> 00:04:21.538
Do you think I can't do it?

32
00:04:24.747 --> 00:04:26.177
I overacted.

33
00:04:26.177 --> 00:04:27.948
So please don't say...

34
00:04:29.148 --> 00:04:30.417
"us"...

35
00:04:31.917 --> 00:04:33.247
so easily.

36
00:04:33.247 --> 00:04:34.857
I asked if you took the bus home.

37
00:04:35.718 --> 00:04:37.357
Do I have to answer that?

38
00:04:37.687 --> 00:04:39.057
No,

39
00:04:40.557 --> 00:04:42.557
- it's not necessary. - Exactly.

40
00:04:46.898 --> 00:04:50.598
You think he knows about our contract?

41
00:04:51.338 --> 00:04:52.468
Yes.

42
00:04:53.038 --> 00:04:58.408
He called you a fake husband.

43
00:04:58.708 --> 00:05:01.648
Why did you marry a fake husband?

44
00:05:02.677 --> 00:05:06.718
Even if he's a stalker, how did he find out?

45
00:05:06.718 --> 00:05:07.817
I'm not sure.

46
00:05:08.857 --> 00:05:11.288
That's something only two of us know.

47
00:05:15.158 --> 00:05:18.167
- Is it because of my phone? - Pardon?

48
00:05:18.328 --> 00:05:20.968
He said that after seeing how I saved you on my phone.

49
00:05:20.968 --> 00:05:24.437
He asked me if you're really my landlord and not a husband.

50
00:05:24.968 --> 00:05:26.067
Yes.

51
00:05:27.107 --> 00:05:30.437
I noticed that you saved me as "Landlord".

52
00:05:30.838 --> 00:05:32.578
It's not common.

53
00:05:32.648 --> 00:05:35.278
Why would you save my number like that?

54
00:05:36.047 --> 00:05:38.747
Then what should I save you as?

55
00:05:39.687 --> 00:05:41.857
There's nothing else.

56
00:05:42.357 --> 00:05:45.758
Well... There's my name.

57
00:05:46.288 --> 00:05:48.497
Se Hee.

58
00:05:50.828 --> 00:05:54.768
Then what did you save me as?

59
00:05:54.768 --> 00:05:56.468
Of course I saved you as...

60
00:06:00.408 --> 00:06:03.778
"Tenant"...

61
00:06:08.117 --> 00:06:10.877
Bo Mi's uncle works at the police station,

62
00:06:11.047 --> 00:06:12.518
so we've informed him.

63
00:06:12.948 --> 00:06:15.057
I'm sure it'll be resolved tomorrow.

64
00:06:15.117 --> 00:06:16.758
What happens to Bok Nam?

65
00:06:16.758 --> 00:06:19.288
He will be locked up.

66
00:06:20.427 --> 00:06:21.528
Okay.

67
00:06:21.727 --> 00:06:23.528
That was close!

68
00:06:23.528 --> 00:06:25.828
Sanchez. He has to pass.

69
00:06:25.828 --> 00:06:27.567
- The ball gets delivered. - It's Giroud.

70
00:06:27.567 --> 00:06:28.937
- It's going in! - Sanchez!

71
00:06:28.937 --> 00:06:30.138
- Goal! - Yes!

72
00:06:32.437 --> 00:06:34.107
What a clean shot.

73
00:06:34.107 --> 00:06:36.578
- Sanchez is amazing. - It's a team goal.

74
00:06:36.578 --> 00:06:37.737
That's right.

75
00:06:37.838 --> 00:06:40.607
Sanchez is hugging his teammates.

76
00:06:40.948 --> 00:06:43.648
It was a counterattack.

77
00:06:44.177 --> 00:06:45.547
It was a perfect goal.

78
00:06:45.547 --> 00:06:47.317
Everything was on beat.

79
00:06:47.518 --> 00:06:48.687
Thank you...

80
00:06:52.427 --> 00:06:53.888
for coming running to me.

81
00:06:56.898 --> 00:06:58.898
For walking down with me.

82
00:07:01.127 --> 00:07:02.297
And for...

83
00:07:04.098 --> 00:07:07.667
calling it our home.

84
00:07:12.648 --> 00:07:15.948
Were you upset...

85
00:07:17.817 --> 00:07:20.747
because I drew a line?

86
00:07:22.317 --> 00:07:27.057
Because I told you not to act like my wife around others?

87
00:07:28.028 --> 00:07:33.198
And because I told you not to call us, "Us"?

88
00:07:35.268 --> 00:07:37.038
Did I upset you?

89
00:07:39.468 --> 00:07:40.567
Yes.

90
00:07:43.278 --> 00:07:44.338
I...

91
00:07:46.348 --> 00:07:48.848
don't want to become your burden.

92
00:07:50.977 --> 00:07:52.648
Unlike others,

93
00:07:53.817 --> 00:07:55.987
our marriage started with an agreement that it'll end.

94
00:07:57.518 --> 00:07:59.458
It provided you a place to live,

95
00:07:59.828 --> 00:08:01.997
and it allowed me to profit by getting rent.

96
00:08:02.427 --> 00:08:04.357
It was a mutual agreement,

97
00:08:06.567 --> 00:08:08.028
but after the contract ends,

98
00:08:09.198 --> 00:08:12.937
the damage might be bigger for you than me.

99
00:08:14.268 --> 00:08:15.877
You're a woman,

100
00:08:16.538 --> 00:08:18.377
and you're younger than me.

101
00:08:19.708 --> 00:08:25.448
That's why the society might look at you more harshly.

102
00:08:26.747 --> 00:08:29.518
I thought I should minimize creating a relationship with you.

103
00:08:30.557 --> 00:08:32.587
I also thought that we should...

104
00:08:33.988 --> 00:08:35.957
avoid sharing anything...

105
00:08:37.258 --> 00:08:38.628
if I can help it.

106
00:08:39.827 --> 00:08:44.038
You were thinking about that the whole time?

107
00:08:49.807 --> 00:08:52.378
About what happens after our marriage is over,

108
00:08:53.508 --> 00:08:57.317
and how it would impact me?

109
00:09:00.148 --> 00:09:03.187
I wouldn't say I thought about it the whole time,

110
00:09:04.587 --> 00:09:07.628
but the thought came to me after our wedding.

111
00:09:08.228 --> 00:09:09.358
Why?

112
00:09:09.797 --> 00:09:12.667
Because I made a promise.

113
00:09:13.998 --> 00:09:16.297
I promised your mother...

114
00:09:17.238 --> 00:09:19.707
I wouldn't make any trouble for you.

115
00:09:22.138 --> 00:09:23.638
I wanted to keep it.

116
00:09:25.677 --> 00:09:28.947
I still want to keep it.

117
00:09:30.047 --> 00:09:32.587
I don't know much about Ji Ho yet,

118
00:09:33.288 --> 00:09:35.417
but at a certain point,

119
00:09:36.758 --> 00:09:38.557
she'll choose a path that makes her happy.

120
00:09:39.687 --> 00:09:42.628
During our marriage, I'll try...

121
00:09:45.067 --> 00:09:46.728
not to be an inconvenience to her choice.

122
00:09:48.898 --> 00:09:52.638
That's all I can promise you.

123
00:10:01.518 --> 00:10:03.947
(Landlord)

124
00:10:05.917 --> 00:10:07.518
(Calling Landlord)

125
00:10:17.528 --> 00:10:18.868
Hello?

126
00:10:19.398 --> 00:10:20.667
It's me.

127
00:10:20.728 --> 00:10:22.898
Yes. I know.

128
00:10:24.498 --> 00:10:25.638
When I...

129
00:10:27.738 --> 00:10:31.748
graduated school and started the assistant writer job,

130
00:10:32.807 --> 00:10:35.077
I got paid 800 dollars a month.

131
00:10:36.748 --> 00:10:38.388
Then my father told me...

132
00:10:39.187 --> 00:10:41.457
to quit right away and to come back home.

133
00:10:42.417 --> 00:10:44.457
He told me to grow spinach instead.

134
00:10:46.628 --> 00:10:48.427
We had a small garden in our backyard.

135
00:10:49.297 --> 00:10:54.228
If we grew spinach for a week, I would make more than that.

136
00:10:55.868 --> 00:10:58.207
No one understood my job,

137
00:10:58.967 --> 00:11:03.408
but do you know how I was able to start it?

138
00:11:06.108 --> 00:11:07.947
I wasn't thinking.

139
00:11:10.177 --> 00:11:12.388
I didn't think to become a great writer.

140
00:11:13.187 --> 00:11:15.087
I didn't think to become famous,

141
00:11:16.988 --> 00:11:18.687
or to succeed.

142
00:11:20.258 --> 00:11:23.457
I never thought about such things.

143
00:11:25.268 --> 00:11:28.337
I came across a script by chance,

144
00:11:29.437 --> 00:11:31.337
and it was so much fun I went crazy over it.

145
00:11:32.738 --> 00:11:34.807
That's why I just jumped in.

146
00:11:37.508 --> 00:11:40.577
It was fun writing every day.

147
00:11:42.417 --> 00:11:44.988
I didn't want to achieve something...

148
00:11:44.988 --> 00:11:46.317
or make something of myself through writing.

149
00:11:46.888 --> 00:11:48.717
It never occurred to me.

150
00:11:49.758 --> 00:11:51.258
That's why...

151
00:11:52.258 --> 00:11:56.498
I won't think about what happens to me two years from now.

152
00:11:58.297 --> 00:12:00.067
If I had,

153
00:12:01.837 --> 00:12:03.937
I probably couldn't have gotten married.

154
00:12:05.908 --> 00:12:07.437
I just...

155
00:12:08.437 --> 00:12:10.738
needed this room right away,

156
00:12:11.337 --> 00:12:13.248
and I liked how safe I felt here.

157
00:12:14.347 --> 00:12:16.748
I didn't want to part ways with Kitty either.

158
00:12:18.388 --> 00:12:19.518
Also,

159
00:12:22.018 --> 00:12:25.658
the landlord looked trustworthy.

160
00:12:27.258 --> 00:12:28.758
That's why I did it.

161
00:12:29.557 --> 00:12:33.728
I liked being a part of this house.

162
00:12:34.628 --> 00:12:37.837
So it's not important to me...

163
00:12:39.038 --> 00:12:41.008
what happens after our marriage.

164
00:12:41.167 --> 00:12:42.778
I don't even think about it.

165
00:12:43.638 --> 00:12:44.947
So...

166
00:12:46.547 --> 00:12:48.278
don't cross a line between us...

167
00:12:50.018 --> 00:12:51.278
on purpose.

168
00:12:53.347 --> 00:12:54.518
Okay.

169
00:12:54.888 --> 00:12:56.118
Don't...

170
00:12:57.988 --> 00:12:59.358
lock your door either.

171
00:13:01.128 --> 00:13:02.258
Okay.

172
00:13:03.557 --> 00:13:07.028
Then, goodnight.

173
00:13:08.337 --> 00:13:11.567
I have something to say too.

174
00:13:12.937 --> 00:13:16.538
Don't call me your landlord.

175
00:13:17.538 --> 00:13:19.577
People might think you live alone.

176
00:13:20.547 --> 00:13:21.847
When you're in front of others,

177
00:13:23.677 --> 00:13:26.687
call me your husband.

178
00:13:27.648 --> 00:13:30.057
Something dangerous might happen again.

179
00:13:30.057 --> 00:13:31.827
Don't let others think you're alone.

180
00:13:33.158 --> 00:13:35.858
For the next two years, you...

181
00:13:37.028 --> 00:13:39.667
belong to this house along with me.

182
00:13:45.337 --> 00:13:46.467
Okay.

183
00:13:47.108 --> 00:13:50.408
Okay. Goodnight, then.

184
00:13:51.847 --> 00:13:55.618
Hey. How did you know I was there?

185
00:13:56.717 --> 00:13:58.288
I didn't have my phone.

186
00:14:43.758 --> 00:14:45.567
(Enjoying the night view on my way back from work)

187
00:14:54.738 --> 00:14:57.508
It's under construction. I don't think I can go any further.

188
00:14:57.837 --> 00:14:59.847
Is there any other way to go up there?

189
00:14:59.847 --> 00:15:01.648
This is the only way to go by car.

190
00:15:02.618 --> 00:15:04.677
What about the way to go by foot?

191
00:15:04.847 --> 00:15:07.717
- This must be the way. - Okay, thank you.

192
00:15:13.028 --> 00:15:15.028
It might take more than 30 minutes though.

193
00:15:58.967 --> 00:16:00.707
Let's go watch soccer.

194
00:16:04.437 --> 00:16:07.307
(Landlord)

195
00:16:10.547 --> 00:16:15.018
(Husband)

196
00:16:16.917 --> 00:16:20.557
(Husband)

197
00:16:22.628 --> 00:16:23.728
Come on.

198
00:16:24.258 --> 00:16:27.228
Let's go to our home.

199
00:16:32.238 --> 00:16:34.908
(Husband)

200
00:16:43.148 --> 00:16:46.717
(Because This Is My First Time Belonging to Somewhere)

201
00:17:06.607 --> 00:17:08.337
(Husband)

202
00:17:11.948 --> 00:17:14.208
(Wife)

203
00:17:18.617 --> 00:17:20.948
(Husband)

204
00:17:34.127 --> 00:17:35.238
Hello?

205
00:17:36.238 --> 00:17:37.268
Hello?

206
00:17:40.038 --> 00:17:41.208
Hello?

207
00:17:44.978 --> 00:17:46.508
You're home.

208
00:17:46.907 --> 00:17:48.478
And why did you call me?

209
00:17:50.147 --> 00:17:51.278
That's...

210
00:17:53.988 --> 00:17:56.557
I called you by mistake while trying to turn off the alarm.

211
00:17:57.258 --> 00:17:59.228
Well...

212
00:18:00.928 --> 00:18:02.028
I see.

213
00:18:04.528 --> 00:18:07.367
Did you have a good night's sleep?

214
00:18:07.928 --> 00:18:10.498
Yes, what about you, Ji Ho?

215
00:18:12.337 --> 00:18:13.438
Me too.

216
00:18:20.948 --> 00:18:23.877
Kitty, how are you here?

217
00:18:24.218 --> 00:18:26.117
She took a taxi and came home alone.

218
00:18:26.647 --> 00:18:30.458
She was crying outside to come in, so I opened the door for her.

219
00:18:35.657 --> 00:18:38.597
She can do that?

220
00:18:40.998 --> 00:18:42.468
Of course not.

221
00:18:44.867 --> 00:18:46.567
It was a joke.

222
00:18:50.508 --> 00:18:53.847
I see, it was a joke.

223
00:18:55.577 --> 00:18:56.718
Yes.

224
00:19:10.097 --> 00:19:12.897
Hello. What's up?

225
00:19:13.268 --> 00:19:14.498
Hello, Bo Mi.

226
00:19:15.067 --> 00:19:17.168
I haven't watched the news yet.

227
00:19:17.168 --> 00:19:18.468
Watch the newscast? Why?

228
00:19:19.337 --> 00:19:20.367
What?

229
00:19:22.907 --> 00:19:24.278
He got caught?

230
00:19:25.008 --> 00:19:28.478
The culprit of the kidnap case that happened in October 30...

231
00:19:28.478 --> 00:19:30.317
got arrested by the police this dawn.

232
00:19:30.877 --> 00:19:34.488
He stalked a woman whom he met through an online game,

233
00:19:34.518 --> 00:19:37.157
kidnapped her, and locked her up for 13 hours.

234
00:19:38.087 --> 00:19:39.887
The police arrested the culprit...

235
00:19:39.928 --> 00:19:42.557
and are investigating on his additional crime.

236
00:19:43.597 --> 00:19:45.367
I still can't believe it.

237
00:19:46.998 --> 00:19:50.297
I had no idea he'd be this kind of person.

238
00:19:50.567 --> 00:19:54.008
You don't even fully know who you are, so it's hard to know others.

239
00:19:55.577 --> 00:19:58.107
Are you really okay to go to work today?

240
00:19:58.877 --> 00:20:01.377
The police could visit the cafe.

241
00:20:02.317 --> 00:20:03.448
I'm okay.

242
00:20:04.248 --> 00:20:07.218
He got arrested, so I'm okay with going to work.

243
00:20:14.827 --> 00:20:17.327
I'll see you at home later.

244
00:20:18.127 --> 00:20:21.768
You'll take a bus home, right?

245
00:20:22.668 --> 00:20:23.738
Yes.

246
00:20:24.367 --> 00:20:26.468
I'll see you later.

247
00:20:27.407 --> 00:20:28.478
Bye.

248
00:20:31.508 --> 00:20:33.278
Bok Nam, that punk.

249
00:20:33.278 --> 00:20:35.317
Ji Ho, are you okay?

250
00:20:35.617 --> 00:20:37.377
I'm okay.

251
00:20:38.047 --> 00:20:40.117
The landlord came to...

252
00:20:40.988 --> 00:20:42.157
I mean...

253
00:20:44.728 --> 00:20:45.988
My husband...

254
00:20:47.327 --> 00:20:48.698
came for me.

255
00:20:49.127 --> 00:20:51.157
I know. I heard it from Soo Ji.

256
00:20:51.668 --> 00:20:53.867
Your husband is amazing.

257
00:20:54.168 --> 00:20:56.198
We all fell for his smile,

258
00:20:56.367 --> 00:20:58.337
and how did he collect all the information?

259
00:20:58.468 --> 00:21:01.577
Exactly. He collected all the evidence...

260
00:21:01.778 --> 00:21:03.637
without my knowledge.

261
00:21:03.978 --> 00:21:05.978
He's so meticulous.

262
00:21:06.248 --> 00:21:07.748
Maybe Won Seok is right.

263
00:21:07.948 --> 00:21:10.948
I heard you have to be incredibly smart to solve that cube.

264
00:21:10.948 --> 00:21:13.347
Your husband set the record of it in the company, right?

265
00:21:14.587 --> 00:21:15.887
No wonder.

266
00:21:16.657 --> 00:21:20.228
He's a meticulous person who never allows mistakes.

267
00:21:40.478 --> 00:21:41.948
My goodness, he took 52 seconds.

268
00:21:42.978 --> 00:21:44.278
Se Hee, you're amazing.

269
00:21:44.278 --> 00:21:45.718
He's the best.

270
00:21:45.718 --> 00:21:47.647
- I know. - It doesn't make sense.

271
00:21:47.718 --> 00:21:50.157
- It's crazy. - It's unbelievable.

272
00:21:50.288 --> 00:21:52.357
- Goodness. - How did he solve it so fast?

273
00:21:53.627 --> 00:21:56.057
- It's impressive. - Goodness.

274
00:21:56.228 --> 00:21:57.258
- He's so cool. - Is he even a human?

275
00:21:58.627 --> 00:22:00.567
- I bet he's not. - How did he do it?

276
00:22:00.567 --> 00:22:03.668
Se Hee, can I have a moment with you if you're done?

277
00:22:03.837 --> 00:22:04.938
It's work-related.

278
00:22:10.407 --> 00:22:12.448
