I know, right?

806
00:55:33.975 --> 00:55:37.506
I wanted to keep it clean until I say goodbye to it though.

807
00:55:38.545 --> 00:55:39.745
"Until I say goodbye"?

808
00:55:40.815 --> 00:55:43.185
Are you trying to sell it to someone?

809
00:55:43.745 --> 00:55:45.085
How much would you like to get from it?

810
00:55:50.386 --> 00:55:51.455
It's a secret.

811
00:56:02.205 --> 00:56:03.665
He's so adorable.

812
00:56:04.136 --> 00:56:07.636
I think I will sleep with you if I stay with you more tonight.

813
00:56:07.676 --> 00:56:08.775
By the way,

814
00:56:08.875 --> 00:56:12.116
the room number was 304. It wasn't 303. The room we stayed, you know.

815
00:56:12.116 --> 00:56:14.475
Did I say I wanted to date you? I said I wanted to sleep with you.

816
00:56:15.446 --> 00:56:16.516
That's right.

817
00:56:17.185 --> 00:56:18.756
I'm evil.

818
00:56:18.986 --> 00:56:21.685
I'm evil and that's why I can survive in this field.

819
00:56:37.165 --> 00:56:38.306
Mr. Ma.

820
00:57:00.895 --> 00:57:01.895
Excuse me,

821
00:57:09.006 --> 00:57:10.065
are you crying?

822
00:57:12.475 --> 00:57:13.475
Why are you...

823
00:57:15.645 --> 00:57:16.846
Are you sick?

824
00:57:29.325 --> 00:57:30.325
Why are you...

825
00:57:32.495 --> 00:57:33.696
Are you sick?

826
00:57:42.659 --> 00:57:44.760
- Mr. Ma! - Mr. Ma!

827
00:57:44.760 --> 00:57:45.829
Come with me.

828
00:57:46.329 --> 00:57:48.670
- Where is he? - Mr. Ma!

829
00:57:48.890 --> 00:57:50.291
- Where is he? - Mr. Ma!

830
00:57:51.698 --> 00:57:52.897
I couldn't find him here.

831
00:57:54.328 --> 00:57:55.967
Then where is he?

832
00:57:56.138 --> 00:57:57.868
- Let's go this way. - Mr. Ma!

833
00:58:02.408 --> 00:58:04.678
If your employees find their boss crying,

834
00:58:05.448 --> 00:58:06.978
it will be really embarrassing.

835
00:58:10.047 --> 00:58:12.817
What is it? Are you really sick or something?

836
00:58:13.217 --> 00:58:14.388
Do you want me to take you to a hospital?

837
00:58:16.217 --> 00:58:17.888
I thought about it,

838
00:58:19.728 --> 00:58:21.428
but I don't think I can give up my work.

839
00:58:22.797 --> 00:58:23.928
What?

840
00:58:24.928 --> 00:58:26.868
I thought about it a lot.

841
00:58:30.967 --> 00:58:33.208
I don't think I can sell my company.

842
00:58:38.547 --> 00:58:40.308
But if I don't do that,

843
00:58:42.647 --> 00:58:44.547
I can't see you anymore.

844
00:58:45.388 --> 00:58:46.448
So...

845
00:58:47.788 --> 00:58:49.288
my heart is...

846
00:58:50.558 --> 00:58:52.158
aching so much.

847
00:58:54.587 --> 00:58:58.527
If you really want to sleep with me, sell your company and quit your job.

848
00:58:59.598 --> 00:59:00.928
Then I will date you.

849
00:59:02.237 --> 00:59:05.067
Just because I told you to...

850
00:59:05.808 --> 00:59:07.837
sell your company away...

851
00:59:08.377 --> 00:59:09.678
Did you take it seriously?

852
00:59:10.337 --> 00:59:12.547
Love matters to me.

853
00:59:13.308 --> 00:59:14.377
But...

854
00:59:15.978 --> 00:59:18.587
my work matters too.

855
00:59:19.487 --> 00:59:21.658
It's really embarrassing.

856
00:59:22.518 --> 00:59:23.717
But...

857
00:59:26.458 --> 00:59:28.428
just the thought of not seeing you made me this way.

858
00:59:38.138 --> 00:59:39.308
Can I...

859
00:59:41.467 --> 00:59:42.507
kiss you now?

860
00:59:45.877 --> 00:59:46.908
What?

861
00:59:48.478 --> 00:59:49.547
What did you say?

862
00:59:49.647 --> 00:59:51.047
Can I kiss you now?

863
00:59:54.118 --> 00:59:57.257
Don't do this to me. I cannot give up my work.

864
00:59:57.958 --> 00:59:59.357
So? Should I not kiss you?

865
00:59:59.857 --> 01:00:02.328
That's not what I meant.

866
01:00:05.627 --> 01:00:06.768
Should I do it then?

867
01:00:08.467 --> 01:00:09.538
Yes.

868
01:00:24.248 --> 01:00:27.888
Most of us misunderstand others.

869
01:00:29.958 --> 01:00:32.627
We shouldn't say,

870
01:00:33.687 --> 01:00:35.598
"I know how you feel."

871
01:00:45.408 --> 01:00:46.937
Where's Mr. Ma?

872
01:00:49.538 --> 01:00:52.208
Let's go to the cafe. I'll buy you a cake.

873
01:00:53.948 --> 01:00:55.748
The reason I'm hopeful is...

874
01:00:56.217 --> 01:00:59.587
because I know people have their limits.

875
01:01:03.257 --> 01:01:04.388
Hi, how are you?

876
01:01:07.857 --> 01:01:09.698
Unless we try hard,

877
01:01:10.828 --> 01:01:13.797
we can't understand each other.

878
01:01:20.638 --> 01:01:21.877
Love exists...

879
01:01:22.578 --> 01:01:24.678
in this kind of world.

880
01:01:29.118 --> 01:01:31.448
Mr. Shim, I heard you are moving to Gyul Mal Ae.

881
01:01:31.547 --> 01:01:32.948
Is that why you stopped our project?

882
01:01:33.388 --> 01:01:35.757
I feel pathetic for wasting two years just because of you.

883
01:01:36.018 --> 01:01:37.487
Let's see how it goes.

884
01:01:38.257 --> 01:01:40.558
As long as you love someone,

885
01:01:41.087 --> 01:01:43.558
we have to try hard.

886
01:01:43.558 --> 01:01:44.928
Here I am! I'm all ready!

887
01:01:46.067 --> 01:01:47.598
What do you think? Do I look good?

888
01:01:51.638 --> 01:01:53.268
- Isn't it pretty? - It is.

889
01:01:53.467 --> 01:01:56.837
Trying hard for the other person...

890
01:01:57.308 --> 01:01:58.607
makes life...

891
01:01:59.208 --> 01:02:02.277
something worth trying.

892
01:02:07.618 --> 01:02:09.817
(We have to work hard as long as we're in love.)

893
01:02:12.928 --> 01:02:15.897
That book must be fun. You're always reading it.

894
01:02:16.897 --> 01:02:19.328
Yes, it's fun.

895
01:02:22.768 --> 01:02:25.507
Are you still mad at me?

896
01:02:25.667 --> 01:02:26.837
What do you mean?

897
01:02:28.237 --> 01:02:30.078
Oh, you mean how I almost ruined myself...

898
01:02:30.078 --> 01:02:32.507
because I tried to hit on you?

899
01:02:34.377 --> 01:02:35.777
I'm really sorry.

900
01:02:37.248 --> 01:02:40.047
I'm letting it go because your fake husband is cool.

901
01:02:40.618 --> 01:02:42.458
I never thought I'd fall by such words.

902
01:02:42.788 --> 01:02:44.518
You have a sweet landlord.

903
01:02:45.058 --> 01:02:46.187
What did he say?

904
01:02:47.027 --> 01:02:50.297
I asked him when he came to pay for the rearview mirror.

905
01:02:50.297 --> 01:02:51.667
I asked him why he married you.

906
01:02:51.728 --> 01:02:54.067
So? What did he say?

907
01:03:33.667 --> 01:03:36.538
Why didn't Mr. Ma come today?

908
01:03:36.708 --> 01:03:38.248
Oh, Mr. Ma...

909
01:03:39.547 --> 01:03:41.478
had another important plan.

910
01:03:43.917 --> 01:03:46.917
Oh, I heard Won Seok is going to work in your company.

911
01:03:47.288 --> 01:03:49.018
Yes, I think he's going to work in my team.

912
01:03:50.788 --> 01:03:51.987
I see.

913
01:03:55.158 --> 01:03:59.328
There are so many stars in the sky tonight.

914
01:04:04.268 --> 01:04:06.308
Is that the Big Dipper?

915
01:04:47.708 --> 01:04:48.917
What's that?

916
01:04:49.817 --> 01:04:51.618
They're our wedding photos.

917
01:04:56.987 --> 01:04:58.788
They look nice.

918
01:04:59.127 --> 01:05:00.687
I forgot about them.

919
01:05:01.127 --> 01:05:03.127
My colleagues worked on them...

920
01:05:03.257 --> 01:05:04.728
as a wedding gift.

921
01:05:10.567 --> 01:05:12.437
It looks quite empty.

922
01:05:13.467 --> 01:05:15.337
You should've called more people.

923
01:05:17.377 --> 01:05:20.547
Actually, I don't have that many friends.

924
01:05:20.607 --> 01:05:22.018
I have only these two.

925
01:05:22.348 --> 01:05:23.877
Two is a lot.

926
01:05:26.817 --> 01:05:28.288
That's not a lot.

927
01:05:28.658 --> 01:05:31.627
I think having just one friend...

928
01:05:32.187 --> 01:05:33.757
is more than enough in life.

929
01:05:35.297 --> 01:05:36.828
That's how I think.

930
01:05:42.237 --> 01:05:43.538
What about love?

931
01:05:47.538 --> 01:05:49.808
Does that apply to love?

932
01:05:51.277 --> 01:05:55.877
I think one love is also enough...

933
01:05:57.147 --> 01:05:58.348
in life.

934
01:06:02.357 --> 01:06:03.558
Sure.

935
01:06:04.288 --> 01:06:07.857
I agree.

936
01:06:09.328 --> 01:06:10.857
In life,

937
01:06:12.027 --> 01:06:13.297
having one love...

938
01:06:15.237 --> 01:06:16.368
is more than enough.

939
01:06:19.168 --> 01:06:22.277
Soo Ji once said that it's better to meet as many boyfriends...

940
01:06:22.277 --> 01:06:24.708
as possible, just like real estate agents.

941
01:06:30.647 --> 01:06:33.288
Ho Rang once said the one you're marrying...

942
01:06:33.288 --> 01:06:36.118
is the love and destiny of life.

943
01:06:37.718 --> 01:06:39.227
But for me,

944
01:06:43.727 --> 01:06:45.798
ever since I was young, I thought having one love...

945
01:06:46.027 --> 01:06:50.538
in life is more than enough.

