948
01:07:30.038 --> 01:07:31.607
(Husband: Nam Se Hee)

949
01:07:31.607 --> 01:07:35.078
(Wife: Jung Min)

950
01:07:39.218 --> 01:07:42.817
I like someone.

951
01:07:44.487 --> 01:07:47.158
- What are you talking about? - Who?

952
01:07:51.567 --> 01:07:52.767
My husband.

953
01:07:54.698 --> 01:07:56.097
Are you kidding me?

954
01:07:56.237 --> 01:07:58.737
What are you doing? Are you rubbing it in?

955
01:07:58.737 --> 01:08:01.237
Then I'm going to say out loud that I love Won Seok.

956
01:08:01.538 --> 01:08:03.807
These wenches. Go to sleep already!

957
01:08:23.828 --> 01:08:26.128
The one and only love in my life...

958
01:08:30.968 --> 01:08:32.368
has begun.

959
01:08:55.597 --> 01:08:59.328
(Because This Is My First Life)

960
01:08:59.597 --> 01:09:03.237
I love being married.

961
01:09:03.368 --> 01:09:05.307
Having a crush on your husband...

962
01:09:05.767 --> 01:09:07.168
after marriage must not be easy.

963
01:09:07.168 --> 01:09:08.277
Is it that obvious?

964
01:09:08.807 --> 01:09:10.338
Is it because of this?

965
01:09:10.338 --> 01:09:12.578
Your immediate superior is that lady.

966
01:09:12.647 --> 01:09:15.177
Are you okay with working here?

967
01:09:15.177 --> 01:09:16.347
I'm getting married!

968
01:09:17.777 --> 01:09:19.987
Are you writing a contract for going out with me?

969
01:09:19.987 --> 01:09:22.317
I like you. I'd love to go out with you.

970
01:09:22.317 --> 01:09:25.987
You and Soo Ji? Your life is ruined now. You can never fix it.

971
01:09:25.987 --> 01:09:27.088
Sang Goo, my darling.

972
01:09:27.088 --> 01:09:29.198
How are you going to make everything alone?

973
01:09:29.198 --> 01:09:31.628
How can I make my daughter-in-law work when she's so precious?

974
01:09:31.628 --> 01:09:33.767
Ji Ho is now getting what in-laws are like.

975
01:09:33.767 --> 01:09:37.298
Is there any way...

976
01:09:37.298 --> 01:09:39.307
to get inside his heart?

